{"id":1235368335,"question_id":415,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 month, 1 week","timestamp":1713408257,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1235368335/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Add Strings","memory":"43.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public String addStrings(String num1, String num2) {\n        StringBuilder result = new StringBuilder();\n        int carry = 0;\n        int i = num1.length() - 1;\n        int j = num2.length() - 1;\n\n        while (i >= 0 || j >= 0 || carry != 0) {\n            int digit1 = (i >= 0) ? num1.charAt(i) - '0' : 0;\n            int digit2 = (j >= 0) ? num2.charAt(j) - '0' : 0;\n            int sum = digit1 + digit2 + carry;\n            result.insert(0, sum % 10);\n            carry = sum / 10;\n            i--;\n            j--;\n        }\n\n        return result.toString();\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"add-strings","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
